	<refsect1 id="description">
		<title>Description</title>
		<para><command>&name;</command> is a text editor with a graphical user
			interface. It can nonetheless be used as a filter: reading data from the
			standard input, and writing it again to the standard output.</para>
	</refsect1>
	<refsect1 id="options">
		<title>Options</title>
		<para>The filename of a file to edit can be supplied directly on the command
			line. The following option is supported:</para>
		<variablelist>
			<varlistentry>
				<term><option>-F</option></term>
				<listitem>
					<para>Enables filter mode.</para>
				</listitem>
			</varlistentry>
		</variablelist>
	</refsect1>
